info:
  version: v1.0
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
  title: ''
paths:
  /followers:
    post:
      description: ''
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Follower'
          description: succeed to register a new follwer
        '400':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
          description: failed to register a new follwer
    put:
      description: ''
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Follower'
          description: succeed to update a follwer
        '400':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {}
          description: failed to update a follwer

servers:
  - url: 'http://example.com'
openapi: 3.0.0


components:
  schemas:
    Follower:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
        fav_number:
          type: integer
      required:
        - name
        - fav_number
      additionalProperties: false
